data.description: Welcome to 1943 Argos Star located in the beautiful, and quiet Arcadia Ridge Community. This home offers 4 bedrooms, 3 baths, island kitchen, a fireplace, open floorplan, and has a pocket office! This home has been upgraded to be ADA accessible. Other upgrades include a custom covered patio, renovated master bath, and beautiful vinyl floors. The community amenities include a swimming pool, jogging/biking trails, and a playground/park for the family to enjoy. This home is conveniently located by new shopping centers, and entertainment, and has easy access to highways 1604, and 211! This home is ready to be loved by new home owners, schedule a tour today!
